1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:08,740
Hai,

3
00:02:09,450 --> 00:02:10,290
over here.

4
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:31,730
I didn't expect you
to still be using a PO box.

5
00:02:32,850 --> 00:02:34,500
I have no choice.

6
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:35,980
If I left a letter

7
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:38,500
addressed to the PSB
at the front desk every day

8
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:40,690
and never actually sent it,

9
00:02:40,690 --> 00:02:43,060
any idiot could tell
there was a problem.

10
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:44,690
A PO box is different.

11
00:02:44,690 --> 00:02:45,890
It's just a string of numbers.

12
00:02:45,890 --> 00:02:47,290
No one at the hotel

13
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:48,690
knows who it's for.

14
00:02:49,690 --> 00:02:50,850
So every day,

15
00:02:50,850 --> 00:02:51,850
you leave a letter

16
00:02:51,850 --> 00:02:52,820
at the hotel front desk?

17
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,340
Hui,

18
00:02:56,130 --> 00:02:58,100
this is your territory.

19
00:02:58,100 --> 00:02:59,500
I wouldn't dare step out the door

20
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,010
without some kind
of protection in place.

21
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:03,410
But it's not every day.

22
00:03:04,570 --> 00:03:05,690
All's fair in war.

23
00:03:06,730 --> 00:03:08,260
I'll keep you guessing.

24
00:03:09,850 --> 00:03:11,100
So, what have you decided?

25
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:11,940
Are we continuing

26
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:12,780
our partnership?

27
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:19,220
Where are you taking me?

28
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,700
(Public Security)

29
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:36,260
(Jiangbin Municipal PSB)

30
00:03:36,540 --> 00:03:37,450
What's the meaning

31
00:03:37,450 --> 00:03:38,290
of bringing me here?

32
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,780
I just want one thing from you.

33
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,980
What will it take to let me go?

34
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:47,660
I told you yesterday.

35
00:03:48,010 --> 00:03:48,980
Did you forget?

36
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:50,940
If you won't do it,

37
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,410
then wait for your prison cell.

38
00:04:06,550 --> 00:04:07,620
Hello, Limin.

39
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:11,210
I'm at the entrance
of the municipal PSB.

40
00:04:14,570 --> 00:04:15,820
Okay.

41
00:04:15,820 --> 00:04:16,660
I'll wait for you.

42
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:20,490
What are you trying to do?

43
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:24,250
The person coming out
in a moment is a cop.

44
00:04:24,250 --> 00:04:26,850
He's in charge
of cough syrup for the city,

45
00:04:26,850 --> 00:04:28,320
and he was my father's subordinate.

46
00:04:29,410 --> 00:04:31,580
Let's settle this right here today.

47
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:32,780
Whatever you have to say,

48
00:04:32,780 --> 00:04:33,850
say it to him.

49
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:37,980
Do you think I'm easily intimidated?

50
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:40,860
Hai,

51
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:42,540
you're getting old.

52
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:45,100
You forgot that my father was a cop.

53
00:04:46,290 --> 00:04:47,490
Fengyang's "Lee Rock".

54
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:50,610
As long as your report letter
reaches the municipal PSB,

55
00:04:50,610 --> 00:04:52,660
it'll be in my hands within half a day.

56
00:04:54,170 --> 00:04:56,020
I don't believe your father

57
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:57,170
can cover everything up.

58
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:00,460
If you don't believe it, try me.

59
00:05:01,850 --> 00:05:03,250
But I'm warning you,

60
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:05,700
if you haven't left
by this time tomorrow,

61
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:07,220
I'll let you experience

62
00:05:07,220 --> 00:05:08,410
what the detention center here

63
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:09,460
is like.

64
00:05:33,490 --> 00:05:34,460
You win.

65
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:36,100
Safe travels,

66
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:36,940
Hai.

67
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,100
- Hui.
- Limin.

68
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:45,940
What brings you here?

69
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,770
Who was that just now?

70
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,700
I was dropping a friend off in the city.

71
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:50,810
I happened to be passing by,

72
00:05:50,810 --> 00:05:51,700
so I came to see you.

73
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:53,660
Alright, dinner's on me.

74
00:05:53,660 --> 00:05:54,500
Great.

75
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:59,220
=Episode 14=
(The Kite)

76
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:04,580
(Jiangbin Municipal People's Hospital)

77
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:05,450
Hello.

78
00:06:06,050 --> 00:06:08,370
Could you please connect me to Room 306?

79
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:09,980
I'm looking for Mr. Tian Jinhai.

80
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:11,730
I'm sorry,

81
00:06:11,740 --> 00:06:13,700
Mr. Tian has already checked out.

82
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:14,980
Checked out?

83
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:15,850
Are you sure?

84
00:06:16,930 --> 00:06:17,770
Yes.

85
00:06:18,850 --> 00:06:19,850
When did he leave?

86
00:06:20,730 --> 00:06:22,580
Mr. Tian left early this morning.

87
00:06:24,410 --> 00:06:25,340
Well,

88
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:26,200
did he leave anything

89
00:06:26,210 --> 00:06:27,080
at the front desk?

90
00:06:28,370 --> 00:06:29,220
No.

91
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:31,610
Thank you.

92
00:06:31,610 --> 00:06:32,460
You're welcome.

93
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:41,500
Songge.

94
00:06:45,610 --> 00:06:46,450
In a bit,

95
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:48,220
after dialysis,
let's go buy some groceries.

96
00:06:48,220 --> 00:06:49,540
I'll cook you something nice.

97
00:06:49,540 --> 00:06:50,730
What's the occasion?

98
00:06:50,730 --> 00:06:52,100
Why are we celebrating?

99
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:52,980
No reason.

100
00:06:53,660 --> 00:06:54,780
I'm just not busy today.

101
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:55,700
A dish I just learned.

102
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,720
I'll show you my skills.

103
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:59,100
Are you free for the rest of the day?

104
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,400
I'm just spending the day with you.

105
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:10,410
That friend of yours

106
00:07:10,410 --> 00:07:11,980
who topped up his account

107
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,410
hasn't come back these past few days?

108
00:07:14,330 --> 00:07:15,780
If he doesn't come, he doesn't come.

109
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:18,410
Just consider it a gift for our opening.

110
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,170
His accent

111
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:22,490
didn't sound local.

112
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:24,690
That's right.

113
00:07:25,370 --> 00:07:27,220
Because he's not a local,

114
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:28,610
he probably went back.

115
00:07:28,610 --> 00:07:29,850
He just came this once,

116
00:07:29,850 --> 00:07:31,020
put in so much money,

117
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,050
and then went back?

118
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:37,250
You're not lying to me, are you?

119
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:38,490
Why would I lie to you?

120
00:07:38,490 --> 00:07:40,170
Songge, you're too tense.

121
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:42,020
Don't worry.

122
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:47,340
Come, let me give you a massage.

123
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:54,220
(Provide coal for the country,
contribute to Fengyang)

124
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:56,860
(Ding Yue Clinic)

125
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:00,540
Sorry, we aren't seeing patients today.

126
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,410
You're Chen Hui's mother, right?

127
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:07,250
You know Hui?

128
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,610
We are good friends.

129
00:08:09,610 --> 00:08:12,100
We met back when he was in Jin'gang.

130
00:08:13,850 --> 00:08:14,810
I never heard

131
00:08:14,810 --> 00:08:16,700
that he had friends in Jin'gang.

132
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:18,020
I was the one

133
00:08:18,020 --> 00:08:19,170
who transferred the equipment

134
00:08:19,170 --> 00:08:20,610
for his roller skating rink to him.

135
00:08:20,610 --> 00:08:22,020
He didn't have a penny then.

136
00:08:22,850 --> 00:08:23,810
He still owes me.

137
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:24,660
If we weren't friends,

138
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:26,460
would I help him without taking money?

139
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:29,050
In that case,

140
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:30,580
you are a benefactor to Hui.

141
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:32,300
I wouldn't say that.

142
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,490
I like your son

143
00:08:33,490 --> 00:08:35,010
very much.

144
00:08:35,010 --> 00:08:36,610
He's smart and capable.

145
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:38,420
You flatter him too much.

146
00:08:39,100 --> 00:08:40,610
You're here to see Hui, right?

147
00:08:40,610 --> 00:08:42,610
He's been staying in the city lately.

148
00:08:42,610 --> 00:08:44,110
He hasn't been
back here for a long time.

149
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:45,490
I've already seen him

150
00:08:45,490 --> 00:08:46,330
in the city.

151
00:08:47,130 --> 00:08:49,490
Today, I made a special trip

152
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:51,250
to visit you and his father.

153
00:09:06,450 --> 00:09:07,300
How is it?

154
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,140
Is it good?

155
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:10,140
It's delicious.

156
00:09:10,530 --> 00:09:12,580
What you cook
is better than what I cook.

157
00:09:12,580 --> 00:09:14,010
If it's so good, why don't you smile?

158
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,580
Is that a new camera?

159
00:09:21,530 --> 00:09:22,850
This is called a Polaroid.

160
00:09:22,850 --> 00:09:24,730
You can see the photo immediately
after taking it.

161
00:09:24,730 --> 00:09:25,570
Let me see.

162
00:09:28,650 --> 00:09:29,820
There's really an image.

163
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:31,340
This is so much fun.

164
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,520
It's a birthday gift for you.

165
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:35,700
But my birthday is still a long way off.

166
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:38,340
The shop only had two left.

167
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:40,010
I was afraid
someone else would grab them.

168
00:09:42,530 --> 00:09:44,420
This is so amazing.

169
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:45,340
Do I press here?

170
00:09:51,180 --> 00:09:52,220
I'll take this call.

171
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:55,730
Hui.

172
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,770
Didn't I make myself clear?

173
00:09:57,770 --> 00:09:59,220
What are you looking for me for?

174
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:01,220
I'm at your house.

175
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:03,940
Are you kidding me?

176
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:06,340
I'm not kidding.

177
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:09,130
Your mother's cooking is delicious.

178
00:10:09,130 --> 00:10:11,180
And your father is right here.

179
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:13,250
Do you want to say something?

180
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:15,370
I have nothing to say.

181
00:10:15,370 --> 00:10:17,130
You two talk.

182
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:20,060
Alright, then I'll just chat
with your father.

183
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:20,980
That's all.

184
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:21,820
Okay, bye.

185
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:24,700
Songge,

186
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:25,580
I need to go out.

187
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:27,050
Go ahead and eat, don't wait for me.

188
00:10:44,580 --> 00:10:45,770
The soup is here.

189
00:10:46,650 --> 00:10:48,220
- Be careful, it's hot.
- Thank you.

190
00:10:48,220 --> 00:10:49,980
Mr. Tian, please take your time.

191
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:51,420
My father-in-law isn't in good health,

192
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,810
so I'll take care of his meal first.

193
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:54,420
Sorry for the trouble, Mrs. Chen.

194
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:55,260
It's no trouble.

195
00:10:56,650 --> 00:10:57,490
Mr. Tian,

196
00:10:57,820 --> 00:10:59,300
- please, don't be formal.
- Alright.

197
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:00,220
Okay.

198
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:01,060
It's delicious.

199
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:05,100
Are you

200
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,420
from Jin'gang?

201
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:10,060
I've been doing business

202
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:11,580
in Jin'gang for over ten years.

203
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,540
In Jin'gang,

204
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:15,130
what business are you in?

205
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:16,690
I'm in trade.

206
00:11:17,650 --> 00:11:18,490
Trade?

207
00:11:18,620 --> 00:11:19,460
What kind of trade?

208
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:20,300
Clothing.

209
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,010
Clothing, huh?

210
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:24,850
Now that you're in Fengyang,

211
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:25,730
where are you staying?

212
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:29,300
I'm staying at that...
What's it called? A guesthouse.

213
00:11:29,940 --> 00:11:30,780
A guesthouse?

214
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:33,710
That must be the Coal Mine Guesthouse.

215
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:34,940
Yes.

216
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:35,940
They told me

217
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:37,700
it's the best hotel in all of Fengyang.

218
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:40,340
Did you see Mr. Yang,

219
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:41,180
the manager?

220
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:42,780
Mr. Yang?

221
00:11:44,130 --> 00:11:45,100
He

222
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:45,940
is very nice

223
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:46,780
and very welcoming.

224
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,880
He was the one who told me

225
00:11:47,930 --> 00:11:48,770
where Hui's mother's

226
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:49,940
clinic was located.

227
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:52,980
He didn't offer to take you

228
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:54,650
for a tour around Fengyang?

229
00:11:55,010 --> 00:11:56,060
He was so enthusiastic.

230
00:11:56,890 --> 00:11:58,730
I told him I was a guest at your home,

231
00:11:58,730 --> 00:11:59,770
but he insisted on waiting

232
00:11:59,770 --> 00:12:00,820
at the guesthouse for me.

233
00:12:01,330 --> 00:12:02,490
He's taking me out tonight.

234
00:12:03,580 --> 00:12:05,060
This person is quite interesting.

235
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:06,420
Yes, he's a good man.

236
00:12:07,650 --> 00:12:08,650
I've got it.

237
00:12:09,850 --> 00:12:10,690
Thank you.

238
00:12:21,370 --> 00:12:22,210
Director Tong,

239
00:12:23,930 --> 00:12:24,770
hurry

240
00:12:24,770 --> 00:12:25,820
and arrange for men

241
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:27,300
to do a night inspection
at the guesthouse.

242
00:12:27,300 --> 00:12:28,140
Check for what?

243
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:29,580
Prostitution.

244
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:31,730
A man came to our house today

245
00:12:31,730 --> 00:12:32,700
named Tian Jinhai.

246
00:12:32,710 --> 00:12:34,010
He's someone Hui met

247
00:12:34,010 --> 00:12:35,370
while working in Jin'gang.

248
00:12:35,370 --> 00:12:36,650
All the equipment

249
00:12:36,650 --> 00:12:38,580
in Hui's roller skating rink

250
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:40,250
was transferred from him.

251
00:12:40,250 --> 00:12:41,460
He didn't ask for money,

252
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:42,370
and it was on credit.

253
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:44,400
Don't you think this whole thing
is too suspicious?

254
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:47,850
Hypothetically, if Hui

255
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:49,340
is really selling cough syrup,

256
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:51,300
then he must have

257
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,850
established that connection in Jin'gang.

258
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:54,490
Then, opening the roller skating rink

259
00:12:54,490 --> 00:12:55,730
is just a front.

260
00:12:56,610 --> 00:12:58,130
(Mistaken Identity)
Tian Jinhai

261
00:12:58,130 --> 00:12:59,300
could very well be Hui's

262
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:01,250
supplier for the cough syrup.

263
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,420
Exactly.

264
00:13:03,650 --> 00:13:04,770
Director Tong,

265
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:05,610
I'm sure

266
00:13:05,610 --> 00:13:07,220
that Tian Jinhai is suspicious.

267
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,850
It's just that we don't
have enough evidence yet,

268
00:13:09,850 --> 00:13:11,490
so you can't arrest him.

269
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:12,460
If we can catch him

270
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:15,980
for solicitation tonight,

271
00:13:16,860 --> 00:13:18,360
then at the very least,

272
00:13:19,410 --> 00:13:21,250
we can detain him for ten days.

273
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:22,820
This time

274
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:24,730
would be incredibly precious to us.

275
00:13:26,130 --> 00:13:27,980
If I want to inspect
the guesthouse tonight,

276
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:30,110
I'll have to notify
the factory security department.

277
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:32,530
No, Yang Baichun

278
00:13:32,530 --> 00:13:33,420
is too well-connected

279
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:34,340
here in Fengyang.

280
00:13:34,940 --> 00:13:37,460
So tonight, all officers
participating in the operation

281
00:13:38,250 --> 00:13:39,700
must hand in

282
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,130
all communication devices.

283
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:42,580
Not a single word must leak out.

284
00:13:43,010 --> 00:13:43,850
Fine.

285
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:45,180
Notify the men.

286
00:13:45,180 --> 00:13:46,980
(Vienna)

287
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:56,450
Hai,

288
00:13:57,010 --> 00:13:59,130
how do you like
the "Little Hong Kong, China?"

289
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:01,700
It's much more fun than our place.

290
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:03,060
If you like it, stay a few more days.

291
00:14:03,060 --> 00:14:05,130
I guarantee you something new every day.

292
00:14:08,250 --> 00:14:09,850
Then, I'll have to come every day.

293
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:12,580
Hai's giving out tips!

294
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:15,650
Listen to me.

295
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:18,980
Request another song for Hai.

296
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,220
When Tian Jinhai comes out,

297
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:21,420
just point him out to us.

298
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,650
We'll carry out the mission,

299
00:14:22,650 --> 00:14:23,770
and you stay in the car.

300
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:33,240
Take your medicine, Dad.

301
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:35,420
Dad.

302
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:40,260
Dad!

303
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,820
Hello, Yun.

304
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:54,700
Are you on duty?

305
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:56,020
What's up?

306
00:14:56,180 --> 00:14:57,460
My father-in-law is in shock.

307
00:14:57,460 --> 00:14:58,820
It looks like kidney failure.

308
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:00,100
Send an ambulance over right away.

309
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:00,940
Okay, right away.

310
00:15:22,730 --> 00:15:24,300
Hello, Fengyang Police Station.

311
00:15:24,300 --> 00:15:25,610
Is Director Chen in?

312
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:26,700
Mrs. Chen?

313
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:27,850
Director Chen has gone out.

314
00:15:27,850 --> 00:15:29,010
Where did he go?

315
00:15:29,010 --> 00:15:30,340
On a mission.

316
00:15:30,340 --> 00:15:31,610
Do you have a message for him?

317
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:44,370
That's Tian Jinhai.

318
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:45,460
Good.

319
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:47,530
Mr. Yang, is everything okay here?

320
00:15:47,530 --> 00:15:49,270
It's safest here in Fengyang.

321
00:15:49,280 --> 00:15:50,120
Don't worry.

322
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,250
Then, I'll get to it.

323
00:15:52,530 --> 00:15:53,370
See you tomorrow.

324
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,730
Don't let anyone see you.

325
00:15:57,590 --> 00:15:58,640
Come, you...

326
00:15:58,850 --> 00:15:59,770
Take the room card.

327
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:00,730
Wait for me in the room.

328
00:16:01,650 --> 00:16:02,490
Director Tong,

329
00:16:02,890 --> 00:16:05,180
Yang Baichun wouldn't be
keeping watch outside, right?

330
00:16:05,180 --> 00:16:06,460
He isn't that sharp.

331
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:08,460
Wait until he fully takes the bait,

332
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:09,430
then we'll close the net.

333
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:11,450
I'm here.

334
00:16:13,300 --> 00:16:14,460
Dr. Ding, where's the patient?

335
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:15,310
In the back room.

336
00:16:15,310 --> 00:16:16,570
Quick, over here!

337
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:21,820
Come on.

338
00:16:29,730 --> 00:16:30,650
Be careful.

339
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:39,980
Dr. Ding,

340
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:40,890
don't worry too much.

341
00:16:40,890 --> 00:16:42,120
We'll be at the hospital soon.

342
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:44,100
Sun,

343
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:45,610
is there a phone in the car?

344
00:16:45,610 --> 00:16:46,730
I need to contact my son.

345
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:48,220
I haven't been able
to get through to him.

346
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:49,060
There is.

347
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,100
Here.

348
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:51,940
Thank you.

349
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:18,800
Strictly implement
provincial government regulations.

350
00:17:18,810 --> 00:17:20,570
Control the number of personnel
working underground.

351
00:17:20,570 --> 00:17:22,290
Ensure the number of workers
in the mining area

352
00:17:22,290 --> 00:17:23,430
does not exceed one hundred people.

353
00:17:24,410 --> 00:17:25,310
Hello, Mrs. Chen.

354
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,530
Hello, Songge.

355
00:17:26,530 --> 00:17:27,860
Is Hui with you?

356
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:29,220
He went out and hasn't come back yet.

357
00:17:29,220 --> 00:17:30,070
What's wrong?

358
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,050
Grandpa fainted.

359
00:17:31,050 --> 00:17:32,420
We're on our way to the hospital.

360
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:33,460
I can't get through to Hui

361
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:34,370
or his father's phone.

362
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:36,180
Mrs. Chen, don't worry yet.

363
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:37,220
I'll head over right now.

364
00:17:57,050 --> 00:17:58,010
Hui.

365
00:17:58,010 --> 00:17:58,850
Where's Tian Jinhai?

366
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:00,250
Who is Tian Jinhai?

367
00:18:00,250 --> 00:18:01,380
I'm asking you, where is Tian Jinhai?

368
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:02,420
The presidential suite.

369
00:18:03,370 --> 00:18:05,050
Who are you talking to?
Show some respect,

370
00:18:05,050 --> 00:18:05,890
you brat.

371
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:08,060
Something's wrong! Quick, let's go!

372
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:17,460
Move!

373
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:18,530
What's happening?

374
00:18:18,530 --> 00:18:19,660
What's going on?

375
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:22,220
Open the door.

376
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:23,540
Open the door!

377
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:28,650
Hui, what are you trying to do?

378
00:18:29,330 --> 00:18:31,210
The police are here. Get out!

379
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:36,020
Director Tong.

380
00:18:36,290 --> 00:18:37,150
Director Tong,

381
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:38,220
what's all this?

382
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:40,940
What were you doing at my house?

383
00:18:40,940 --> 00:18:41,810
Take your hand off me.

384
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:42,980
Let go.

385
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:44,900
You think I'm easily intimidated?

386
00:18:45,180 --> 00:18:46,330
Take me to the station.

387
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:49,140
Put on a show,
and then maybe I'll believe you.

388
00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:50,340
Good thing you came to me now.

389
00:18:50,570 --> 00:18:51,620
Otherwise, tomorrow,

390
00:18:51,620 --> 00:18:53,420
I'd have gone
to your old man for a showdown.

391
00:18:55,730 --> 00:18:56,570
This...

392
00:18:58,220 --> 00:18:59,060
Director Tong.

393
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:00,770
Nobody move.

394
00:19:00,770 --> 00:19:01,620
Police.

395
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:03,180
What's this all about?

396
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:04,940
What are you doing?

397
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:06,010
Routine inspection.

398
00:19:06,730 --> 00:19:07,770
You two, check that room.

399
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:09,330
Mr. Tong.

400
00:19:09,330 --> 00:19:10,380
Sit down.

401
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:12,900
Officer,

402
00:19:13,380 --> 00:19:15,010
is it illegal for friends

403
00:19:15,010 --> 00:19:16,290
to have a drink and a chat?

404
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:17,220
It's not illegal.

405
00:19:18,330 --> 00:19:19,900
But you must cooperate with us.

406
00:19:21,090 --> 00:19:21,930
Name?

407
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:24,410
Tian Jinhai.

408
00:19:24,420 --> 00:19:25,570
Show me your identification.

409
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:27,770
This must be a misunderstanding.

410
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:29,380
How can I do business like this?

411
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:31,290
How am I supposed
to explain this to the mine?

412
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:32,220
Shut up.

413
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,380
None of your business.

414
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:34,220
Wait outside.

415
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:37,820
Call me if you need anything.

416
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:46,530
Mr. Tong, look at what you've done.

417
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,720
Okay, thank you for your cooperation.

418
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:55,780
Fall out.

419
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:07,840
Hello?

420
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:09,380
Why haven't you come to pick me up?

421
00:20:09,380 --> 00:20:10,530
I'm about to get off work.

422
00:20:10,530 --> 00:20:11,730
Go back by yourself.

423
00:20:11,730 --> 00:20:12,770
I'm busy today.

424
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:14,220
Are you out carousing again?

425
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,420
With whom would I be carousing?

426
00:20:16,770 --> 00:20:18,620
The police station
is doing a night inspection.

427
00:20:18,620 --> 00:20:20,310
The police station
is doing a night inspection?

428
00:20:21,090 --> 00:20:22,620
Is Chen Hongbing there?

429
00:20:22,620 --> 00:20:23,570
Haven't seen him.

430
00:20:23,570 --> 00:20:24,410
Director Tong.

431
00:20:25,010 --> 00:20:25,850
Director Tong.

432
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:27,980
Where is he?

433
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,140
I see him. He just got here.

434
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:29,980
What's wrong?

435
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:37,620
(Fengyang Coal Mine Guesthouse)

436
00:20:40,090 --> 00:20:40,930
Dad.

437
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:45,980
Tell me.

438
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:47,660
Why are you here?

439
00:20:48,620 --> 00:20:49,810
I'm here discussing business.

440
00:20:49,810 --> 00:20:51,420
You didn't do it sooner or later.

441
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:52,980
Why does it have to be at this time?

442
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:53,940
At what time?

443
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:55,700
- Well...
- Stop playing dumb with me!

444
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:56,980
Get out of the way!

445
00:20:56,980 --> 00:20:58,700
- Tell me!
- Hongbing!

446
00:20:58,700 --> 00:20:59,940
You're lying to me.

447
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:00,860
Your father was taken by Ding Yue

448
00:21:00,860 --> 00:21:03,220
to the municipal hospital
for emergency treatment!

449
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,660
- When?
- Just now!

450
00:21:06,250 --> 00:21:07,140
The ambulance is here.

451
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:12,220
- Careful.
- Slow down.

452
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,570
Mrs. Chen,

453
00:21:15,570 --> 00:21:17,140
the emergency doctor is ready.

454
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:26,260
Mrs. Chen.

455
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:28,460
The blood test results are out.

456
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:32,740
They're out.

457
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:35,010
Go check if the CT results are out yet.

458
00:21:35,010 --> 00:21:35,890
Two vials of erythropoietin,

459
00:21:35,890 --> 00:21:36,730
one of lanthanum carbonate.

460
00:21:36,730 --> 00:21:37,620
Hurry and pay for the medicine.

461
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:38,490
I'm waiting inside.

462
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:39,330
I'm going now.

463
00:21:40,810 --> 00:21:42,180
Adrenaline, 2 mg,

464
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:43,020
IV push.

465
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:45,700
Patient is in V-fib.

466
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:46,640
Prepare to defibrillate.

467
00:21:51,980 --> 00:21:52,980
Second shock.

468
00:21:55,620 --> 00:21:56,530
Third shock.

469
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:09,900
Why did you stop?

470
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,380
The phone has been vibrating.

471
00:22:13,940 --> 00:22:14,780
(Incoming Call: Songge)
It's Mom.

472
00:22:15,480 --> 00:22:17,090
Hello, Mom?

473
00:22:17,630 --> 00:22:19,050
- Don't worry.
- Give me the phone.

474
00:22:19,050 --> 00:22:20,730
- Give me the phone!
- You're too loud.

475
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:22,660
Speak slowly, Mom.

476
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:24,180
Don't rush. Go ahead.

477
00:22:24,180 --> 00:22:25,020
Hui...

478
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:28,090
Your grandpa...

479
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:32,980
He's gone.

480
00:22:34,090 --> 00:22:35,090
He's gone.

481
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:42,780
(Jiangbin Municipal People's Hospital)

482
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:45,700
He's gone.

483
00:22:47,230 --> 00:22:48,250
What did your mother say?

484
00:22:49,770 --> 00:22:50,700
What did she say?

485
00:22:53,570 --> 00:22:54,530
Grandpa is gone.

486
00:24:22,460 --> 00:24:24,540
(In mourning)

487
00:24:24,540 --> 00:24:30,820
(Deeply mourning Mr. Chen Xuefeng)

488
00:24:30,820 --> 00:24:34,060
(In mourning, deeply mourning)

489
00:24:40,990 --> 00:24:41,930
Take it easy, Chief Liu.

490
00:24:45,140 --> 00:24:45,980
Kang Limin.

491
00:24:47,730 --> 00:24:48,570
Liu Na.

492
00:25:07,090 --> 00:25:07,930
Hui,

493
00:25:08,660 --> 00:25:10,050
you need to get well soon.

494
00:25:10,660 --> 00:25:11,500
You said

495
00:25:12,050 --> 00:25:14,050
you'd fly kites with me.

496
00:25:23,250 --> 00:25:25,180
My mom isn't home.

497
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:27,810
Let's go! Let's go fly a kite!

498
00:25:27,810 --> 00:25:29,730
Let's go!

499
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,940
(Filial Piety)

500
00:25:44,700 --> 00:25:45,540
Hui,

501
00:25:46,530 --> 00:25:48,140
I heard your grandfather passed away.

502
00:25:48,140 --> 00:25:49,940
I came to see you.

503
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:50,940
This condolence gift

504
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:52,380
(Condolence money)
is for your grandfather.

505
00:25:54,090 --> 00:25:55,810
Get the heck back
to where you came from.

506
00:25:55,810 --> 00:25:57,490
Stop putting up a front.

507
00:25:57,490 --> 00:25:58,380
You said your father

508
00:25:58,380 --> 00:25:59,700
was the Fengyang's Lee Rock.

509
00:25:59,700 --> 00:26:01,490
I thought he
really embezzled 500 million.

510
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:04,700
Turns out he's a good cop.

511
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:06,530
You were bluffing me
from the very start.

512
00:26:06,530 --> 00:26:08,090
You even said you
weren't afraid of my report letter.

513
00:26:08,090 --> 00:26:09,620
I'm glad I didn't believe your nonsense.

514
00:26:09,620 --> 00:26:10,700
I'm giving you two choices.

515
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:13,460
First, keep selling goods for me.

516
00:26:14,330 --> 00:26:17,250
Second, get ready to go to prison.

517
00:26:17,810 --> 00:26:19,730
Why won't you just leave me alone?

518
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:21,490
I said I'm not doing it.

519
00:26:21,490 --> 00:26:23,420
I'm not doing it anymore!

520
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:26,460
If you want out, you're out?

521
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:27,660
If you want to quit, you quit?

522
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,290
To tell you the truth,

523
00:26:29,290 --> 00:26:30,380
all my money

524
00:26:30,380 --> 00:26:31,460
was gambled away.

525
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,490
I lost it all.

526
00:26:32,490 --> 00:26:33,940
I'm still millions in debt.

527
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:35,530
So, you have to do this for me.

528
00:26:35,530 --> 00:26:36,940
Don't test my patience.

529
00:26:37,850 --> 00:26:38,700
I really don't know

530
00:26:38,700 --> 00:26:39,730
what I might do.

531
00:26:45,290 --> 00:26:46,490
Give me two days.

532
00:26:47,220 --> 00:26:49,050
I need to finish
the funeral at home first.

533
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,780
Fine.

534
00:26:53,460 --> 00:26:54,810
Out of respect for the dead.

535
00:27:46,010 --> 00:27:46,850
Limin,

536
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:49,330
Tian Jinhai

537
00:27:49,330 --> 00:27:51,250
got a real scare from us this time.

538
00:27:51,250 --> 00:27:52,660
I suspect

539
00:27:52,660 --> 00:27:54,620
he won't give us another chance.

540
00:27:54,620 --> 00:27:55,620
Trying to follow

541
00:27:55,620 --> 00:27:57,330
Tian Jinhai's lead for evidence

542
00:27:57,330 --> 00:27:58,310
will be hard now.

543
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,180
In that case,

544
00:27:59,180 --> 00:28:01,810
I'll file a report with the Bureau
to pull Tian Jinhai's file

545
00:28:01,810 --> 00:28:03,620
and see if we can find a breakthrough.

546
00:28:03,940 --> 00:28:06,620
The key is that we have to
get this cleared up quickly.

547
00:28:06,620 --> 00:28:07,900
If this continues,

548
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:09,330
Hongbing's family

549
00:28:09,330 --> 00:28:10,380
will fall apart.

550
00:28:12,380 --> 00:28:13,220
Hongbing.

551
00:28:13,810 --> 00:28:14,730
Okay.

552
00:28:14,730 --> 00:28:15,660
Let's leave it at that.

553
00:28:16,940 --> 00:28:17,780
Thank you.

554
00:28:19,490 --> 00:28:21,060
Director Tong, Limin.

555
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:22,500
How is it?

556
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:23,740
Is everything arranged?

557
00:28:25,090 --> 00:28:26,530
It's mostly settled.

558
00:28:26,530 --> 00:28:28,700
Hongbing, does Ding Yue know

559
00:28:29,840 --> 00:28:30,980
about your suspicion of Hui?

560
00:28:35,090 --> 00:28:36,460
Let me give you a heads-up.

561
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:37,420
Regarding Ding Yue,

562
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:38,310
you need to be

563
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:39,460
fully prepared mentally.

564
00:28:40,090 --> 00:28:41,290
Prepared for what?

565
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:43,090
We are the police.

566
00:28:43,570 --> 00:28:45,730
If my son really broke the law,

567
00:28:45,730 --> 00:28:47,180
you should arrest him

568
00:28:47,180 --> 00:28:48,060
and sentence him.

569
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,750
Once he's reformed in the future,

570
00:28:51,180 --> 00:28:52,090
he'll still be my son.

571
00:28:56,660 --> 00:28:57,570
Master,

572
00:28:57,570 --> 00:28:58,570
there's something

573
00:28:58,570 --> 00:28:59,860
I should tell you.

574
00:29:00,490 --> 00:29:03,810
Chief Liu has submitted his resignation
to the Bureau.

575
00:29:11,570 --> 00:29:12,410
Chief Liu.

576
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,380
Director Chen, what's wrong?

577
00:29:14,380 --> 00:29:15,770
Why are you being so mysterious?

578
00:29:17,140 --> 00:29:18,180
I heard

579
00:29:19,010 --> 00:29:20,490
you submitted your resignation.

580
00:29:25,330 --> 00:29:26,660
Is it because of your health?

581
00:29:28,730 --> 00:29:30,860
My health is getting worse lately.

582
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:32,000
I can't do this job anymore.

583
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:37,490
With you leaving,

584
00:29:37,490 --> 00:29:39,490
it's quite a loss

585
00:29:39,490 --> 00:29:40,460
for our police force.

586
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:42,540
It's fine.

587
00:29:43,330 --> 00:29:44,770
There are still other comrades.

588
00:29:47,530 --> 00:29:48,570
Take care of yourself.

589
00:29:51,860 --> 00:29:52,700
Director Chen,

590
00:29:53,290 --> 00:29:55,250
do you really think

591
00:29:55,250 --> 00:29:56,420
it was Hui?

592
00:30:01,940 --> 00:30:03,010
I'm worried it was him.

593
00:30:09,940 --> 00:30:11,620
I no longer have the standing

594
00:30:11,620 --> 00:30:12,940
to be involved in this matter.

595
00:30:14,090 --> 00:30:15,700
It's in God's hands.

596
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:17,110
You shouldn't worry too much either.

597
00:30:20,090 --> 00:30:21,050
If I can,

598
00:30:22,730 --> 00:30:24,140
I'd like to help you one last time.

599
00:30:27,530 --> 00:30:28,490
Thank you.

600
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:39,740
(In mourning, rest in peace)

601
00:31:34,770 --> 00:31:35,610
Grandpa,

602
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,250
when we meet again,

603
00:31:42,180 --> 00:31:43,660
I'll definitely fly kites with you.

604
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:49,180
Your grandfather

605
00:31:51,290 --> 00:31:53,090
was a hero of our Fengyang Mine,

606
00:31:54,620 --> 00:31:55,460
a role model.

607
00:31:55,460 --> 00:31:57,900
(In mourning, deeply mourning)

608
00:31:59,530 --> 00:32:00,730
When we were young,

609
00:32:02,770 --> 00:32:04,420
your grandfather taught us

610
00:32:07,090 --> 00:32:08,460
to be upright

611
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:11,140
and honorable.

612
00:32:15,490 --> 00:32:16,330
Dad,

613
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:18,090
I am a police officer.

614
00:32:19,860 --> 00:32:21,140
I won't let this family

615
00:32:22,620 --> 00:32:23,860
have any stain on its name.

616
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:29,700
Dad,

617
00:32:30,810 --> 00:32:32,050
rest in peace.

618
00:33:20,090 --> 00:33:23,250
♪You ask what is outside the window♪

619
00:33:23,910 --> 00:33:26,900
♪You ask what color the light is♪

620
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:31,610
♪You say hope is a dancing bubble♪

621
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:36,760
♪So colorful and free♪

622
00:33:37,330 --> 00:33:42,270
♪Yet popping at a single touch♪

623
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:48,880
♪So I hope this world protects me♪

624
00:33:50,460 --> 00:33:55,540
♪Just like when we
were innocent children♪

625
00:33:57,640 --> 00:34:00,610
♪Back then, the distance was in sight♪

626
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,850
♪The road had no end♪

627
00:34:03,970 --> 00:34:06,700
♪Say "see you tomorrow"♪

628
00:34:06,990 --> 00:34:12,030
♪And there would surely be a future♪

629
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:15,930
♪The moonlight shines on the bed♪

630
00:34:16,160 --> 00:34:19,370
♪Memories tucked in an old pocket♪

631
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:22,980
♪Wind whistling through empty sleeves♪

632
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:27,260
♪Just pretend
you're holding my hand again♪

633
00:34:27,260 --> 00:34:30,610
♪The moonlight shines on the bed♪

634
00:34:30,610 --> 00:34:33,680
♪Flames flicker, the heart feels hollow♪

635
00:34:33,950 --> 00:34:37,410
♪Climbing high towers,
wandering alleyways♪

636
00:34:37,680 --> 00:34:52,530
♪The four seasons remain,
but people have grown old♪
